{"tid":1531620,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實跳閘會唔會秋後","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T20:41:42.000Z","uid":155265,"like":0,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"619c7115d3d51ffe034ca4cb6bfbc02da495cd6f","tid":1531620,"uid":155265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:36:03.000Z","msg":"小弟唔驚跳閘果下 只係驚會秋後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d262624662d1e818fbb70d0160b7ce22b6fdf7e3","tid":1531620,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71bae3ee28250e4aca14a8344acc4620b508e0b7","tid":1531620,"uid":155265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲解答下"},{"pid":"aff41355609b984ae96c119ee6c4e62736ab739e","tid":1531620,"uid":47548,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩,頂多咪罰幾舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5669ffbede4aef0922f46d7b1f6b1a02438f2f02","tid":1531620,"uid":315566,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"619c7115d3d51ffe034ca4cb6bfbc02da495cd6f","tid":1531620,"uid":155265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:36:03.000Z","msg":"小弟唔驚跳閘果下 只係驚會秋後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /